<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>mappers</span><span class="token punctuation">&gt;</span></span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><div class="language-xml line-numbers-mode" data-ext="xml"><pre class="language-xml"><code><span class="token comment">&lt;!-- 使用映射器接口实现类的完全限定类名 --&gt;</span>
<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>mappers</span><span class="token punctuation">&gt;</span></span>
